data.description:
As you search for the ideal location to host your next event, we invite you to discover for yourself all that this legendary place has to offer. From Hernando De Soto and his search for the elusive Fountain of Youth in 1539 to today's Fortune 500 live in pursuit of organizational excellence, Florida's historic Safety Harbor Resort & Spa has served as a place of inspiration, imagination, and education for those who seek the extraordinary.

Overlooking the peaceful waters of Tampa Bay, you will discover a one of a kind destination rich in history and revered for world class hospitality. From a board meeting of 10 to an international gathering of 1,000 the historic Safety Harbor Resort and Spa offers a distinctive distraction free environment for the most demanding meetings and events.

Beautiful Waterfront Location on Tampa Bay
30,000 Square Feet of Flexible Meeting Space
172 Spacious Business-ready Guest Rooms & Suites
Florida's Only Natural Mineral Springs Spa
Acres of Inspiration Outdoor Spaces Ideal for Team Building
20 Minutes from Tampa International Airport
Walk to Popular Shopping, Dining, and Entertainment
A Florida Heritage Landmark


And while we can't promise our water will keep you forever young, we are confident your next meeting at the Historic Safety Harbor Resort will be fondly remembered for a very long time.
